{"tid":2139742,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅湖懲教所外籍在囚人士計劃挑戰管方 管方已監察","createTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T13:47:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3ab908db394ce1ecccdbd90f741cda73c11a4fc7","tid":2139742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/125718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F125718&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=45a7d2c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/125718</a><br />\n<br />\n懲教署表示，羅湖懲教所早上有59名在囚人士在飯堂早飯期間，其中21名外籍在囚人士不滿奶茶口味，集體要求即時更換，否則拒絕離開飯堂。懲教人員按程序試味，發覺並無不妥。在區域應變隊支援下，懲教人員發出最後警告後，相關在囚人士陸續離開飯堂。現時該21名在囚人士正被隔離調查，署方會密切監察院所情況，並作適當部署。懲教署表示，羅湖懲教所近日得悉部分外籍在囚人士，計劃在衣食住行各方面挑戰管方，煽動在囚人士情緒，管方監察有關人士，懲教人員會保持高度戒備，防止任何在囚人士利用疫情下的不安情緒，製造事端。<br />\n<br />\n2020-08-04 20:54:25"},{"pid":"23e53b47a49f9a15361a10cfab07b1bbbeaaf213","tid":2139742,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f984360e35edd78e7cd538e4016c14fdb42551","tid":2139742,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"點解有20幾個外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2d99ed63629255e6f6f010fbb57252de3f4570","tid":2139742,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:08:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5930db07cabc10be902f40ec0663807cae3b1bc4","tid":2139742,"uid":33635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"又煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4a8466d1386763496d38782f670aac8039877f","tid":2139742,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f984360e35edd78e7cd538e4016c14fdb42551","tid":2139742,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"點解有20幾個外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a0f1e6116edb22e04eefdce283629a638c15aa9","tid":2139742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/04/P2020080400668.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202008%2F04%2FP2020080400668.htm&d=dUSYmziiyXe0H9uVu%2B4Yd7np9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=6b242a51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202008/04/P2020080400668.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n懲教署打擊在囚人士非法活動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  ​懲教署今日（八月四日）採取行動打擊羅湖懲教所在囚人士非法活動。<br />\n<br />\n  羅湖懲教所近日接獲情報，得悉部分外籍在囚人士計劃在衣食住行各方面挑戰管方，煽動在囚人士的情緒。管方隨即監察目標人物的活動情況。<br />\n  <br />\n  今日上午約九時四十分，五十九名在囚人士在飯堂早飯期間，當中有二十一名外籍在囚人士不滿奶茶的口味，並集體要求即時更換，否則拒絕離開飯堂。懲教人員按既定程序試味，發覺並無不妥。在區域應變隊的支援下，在懲教人員發出最後警告後，相關在囚人士在上午十時三十分陸續離開飯堂。現時該二十一名在囚人士正被隔離調查。署方會密切監察院所情況並作出適當部署。<br />\n<br />\n  該署按法例要求為在囚人士提供簡單而有益健康的食物。膳食由合資格的膳食工藝教導員指導下烹調，並由院所管理人員檢查及試味後派發。在囚人士的個人喜好或口味並不會被納入考慮之列。<br />\n<br />\n  懲教人員會保持高度戒備，防止任何在囚人士利用現時在囚人士在疫情下的不安情緒，製造事端。<br />\n<br />\n  羅湖懲教所是一所中度設防監獄，羈押女性成年在囚人士，主要為定罪在囚人士。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年8月4日（星期二）<br />\n香港時間19時58分"},{"pid":"c1a30d435147ad54a28389da2221d7960abc11e1","tid":2139742,"uid":275724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f984360e35edd78e7cd538e4016c14fdb42551","tid":2139742,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"點解有20幾個外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:13:39.000Z","msg":"南亞人"},{"pid":"625b0eab033bdaa4acdb5e605bc992a81a9ef787","tid":2139742,"uid":11454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"故事任佢up<br />\n屎水沖奶茶<br />\n迫你飲試味<br />\n唔飲就淋<br />\n打完返倉<br />\n邊個知真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9054f5fd5c35c08ce1797c45622a1dc9b05187dd","tid":2139742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59f984360e35edd78e7cd538e4016c14fdb42551","tid":2139742,"uid":362346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:07:51.000Z","msg":"點解有20幾個外國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:17:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7964d3828a838fe7bc54120f70239d93b0963c8","tid":2139742,"uid":244797,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"發放得出嚟咁通常個原因都係流嘅<br />\n又話者奶茶只係用嚟借題發揮<br />\n仲有犯飲嗰杯同職員試嗰杯唔同好正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42b3a9e0afd708418a522b8aedc3f43e37289e7","tid":2139742,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T13:26:31.000Z","msg":"懲教署點都易過警察啦下麻?"},{"pid":"2184b615b580a07d3f3b44fd94a545ee3d322c4b","tid":2139742,"uid":37297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7964d3828a838fe7bc54120f